'''Rikrieshan''' a haktiviti a leja, ah leja a diskreshaneri taim. Di niid fi du sinting fi rikrieshan, expres az "du sinting bifuo sinting du yu," a wah isenshal eliment a yuuman bayloji ah saikaloji. Rikrieshanal aktiviti noftaim du fi injaiment, amyuuzment, ar pleja ah kansida fi bi "fon".

